{"tid":1293053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有片段顯示警車旁放有磚頭　警方：移離潛在危險品","createTime":"2019-07-07T14:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T08:22:39.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7a38c1c8484ab2cb517616d163c8be26c63ea110","tid":1293053,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:33:53.000Z","msg":"網上流傳片段及相片，顯示高鐵西九龍站附近，有一輛警車旁邊放有多塊磚頭，當時警車車門打開。另外有片段可見，有多名穿上黑色背心、白色上衣的疑似警員，互相用人手運送懷疑是磚頭的物件。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆本台查詢稱，由於九龍區今日舉行公眾活動，警員於活動路線一帶巡查，發現匯民道一個工地有構成對公眾有潛在危險的物品，獲工地主管同意後，警員遂移離部分物品。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467095-20190707.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467095-20190707.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JldAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=4d5d0a14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467095-20190707.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=95143fb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467095-20190707.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6f3e67c221b11603498241129b1df9b526514c89","tid":1293053,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e795d11c8416d4bb3c14ac861d379a661d09a29","tid":1293053,"uid":2949,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:38:00.000Z","msg":"潛在危險人物移離潛在危險品"},{"pid":"266075dcb8e1a8d77441084f7597d33b9e28881a","tid":1293053,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca3d880a716d42fb35378140a3b41570579acb3","tid":1293053,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hk